title: File:Admiralty Chart No 1378 Honolulu Harbour, Published 1881.jpg
author: United Kingdom Hydrographic Office
description: Nautical chart of Honolulu Harbour. Chiefly from a survey by Navg. Lieut. G.E.G Jackson, 1880, with additions from surveys made in 1856 and 1863 by T.A. Hull, Master, and Capt. G.H. Richards, H.M.S. Hecate. Not current - not to be used for navigation!
